claim.claim-text:
A device comprising:
a substrate (12);
an integrated circuit (IC) die (18) attached to the substrate on one side, and having an active side;
a plurality of thermally and electrically conductive legs (28-32), each of the legs attached to the active side and resulting in external contacts (58, 60, 62) that are separated from each other;_and
an encapsulating material (46) formed around the substrate, the IC die, and a portion of the legs, the external contacts are exposed, and one of the external contacts (58) conducts a signal from a transistor (90) in the IC die.
